{"tid":1800904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只要在法院贏一場，場扙一定贏","createTime":"2019-12-28T09:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T09:12:49.000Z","uid":288154,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26709e127f8e6fc7fe2729e73b25f893de4733b6","tid":1800904,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"法官過去判案，陳明不考慮政治訴求是合理使用暴力。<br />\n所以我哋要陳述清楚比法官明白，市民用武力發動革命是被動的，<br />\n<strong>全是政府先向市民宣戰</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n現在開始，每次上法院，必陳明：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">法官閣下，<br />\n市民和平遊行請願【五大訴求】！<br />\n政府漠視和平請願訴求，<strong>612</strong>拒接見立法會議員，<br />\n以為有三萬暴兵可實行任何暴政！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民用武力是<strong>被動</strong>的，是<strong>612</strong>暴兵<strong>先</strong>用暴力向市民<strong>宣戰</strong>！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n政府以為法院上一定贏<br />\n請手足合力集齊判決書，一齊再想出更多辦法贏在法院<br />\n只要在法院贏一場，場扙一定贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a874e5f4e888e3b27b5afc954804578d5bc114e0","tid":1800904,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"你試吓上庭去同彭寶琴講<br />\n<br />\n10年後再見返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e753707662feb1f9a7f8bb23ba7b5df8f1838f4b","tid":1800904,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"嗡乜撚野啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學畢業未"},{"pid":"c733c01f39aa722e81923db8ff0328a86473e07b","tid":1800904,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a874e5f4e888e3b27b5afc954804578d5bc114e0","tid":1800904,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"你試吓上庭去同彭寶琴講<br />\n<br />\n10年後再見返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"你不如學美國革命黨好過啦"},{"pid":"ee5e93f4eb736b55c7e